    "markdown": "---\ntitle: Repeated-Measures ANOVA\nsubtitle: Practice Problems for PSY 241\nauthor: Guenther, Benjamin A.\nproject:\n  type: website\n  output-dir: docs\nformat: \n  html:\n    html-math-method: mathjax\n    self-contained-math: false\n    embed-resources: false\njupyter: python3\n---\n\n\n\nGiven the following within-subjects data, use a repeated-measures ANOVA with $\\alpha = {0.01}$\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_2943e\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_2943e_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >ID</th>\n      <th id=\"T_2943e_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >A</th>\n      <th id=\"T_2943e_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >B</th>\n      <th id=\"T_2943e_level0_col3\" class=\"col_heading level0 col3\" >C</th>\n      <th id=\"T_2943e_level0_col4\" class=\"col_heading level0 col4\" >D</th>\n      <th id=\"T_2943e_level0_col5\" class=\"col_heading level0 col5\" >E</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" >79</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row0_col2\" class=\"data row0 col2\" >53</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row0_col3\" class=\"data row0 col3\" >49</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row0_col4\" class=\"data row0 col4\" >49</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row0_col5\" class=\"data row0 col5\" >61</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" >71</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row1_col2\" class=\"data row1 col2\" >69</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row1_col3\" class=\"data row1 col3\" >64</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row1_col4\" class=\"data row1 col4\" >54</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row1_col5\" class=\"data row1 col5\" >56</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row2_col1\" class=\"data row2 col1\" >56</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row2_col2\" class=\"data row2 col2\" >58</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row2_col3\" class=\"data row2 col3\" >68</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row2_col4\" class=\"data row2 col4\" >77</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row2_col5\" class=\"data row2 col5\" >59</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row3_col0\" class=\"data row3 col0\" >4</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row3_col1\" class=\"data row3 col1\" >59</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row3_col2\" class=\"data row3 col2\" >79</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row3_col3\" class=\"data row3 col3\" >79</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row3_col4\" class=\"data row3 col4\" >45</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row3_col5\" class=\"data row3 col5\" >31</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row4_col0\" class=\"data row4 col0\" >5</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row4_col1\" class=\"data row4 col1\" >81</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row4_col2\" class=\"data row4 col2\" >47</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row4_col3\" class=\"data row4 col3\" >56</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row4_col4\" class=\"data row4 col4\" >35</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row4_col5\" class=\"data row4 col5\" >41</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row5_col0\" class=\"data row5 col0\" >6</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row5_col1\" class=\"data row5 col1\" >80</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row5_col2\" class=\"data row5 col2\" >74</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row5_col3\" class=\"data row5 col3\" >69</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row5_col4\" class=\"data row5 col4\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_2943e_row5_col5\" class=\"data row5 col5\" >72</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n```\n<br>Summary statistics for these data:<br>\n                             $G = {1774} \\quad \\Sigma X^2 = {113648} \\quad k = {5} \\quad N = {30}$ <br>\n                             \n$T_{A} = {426} \\quad SS_{A} = {614.0}$ <br>\n$T_{B} = {380} \\quad SS_{B} = {793.33}$ <br>\n$T_{C} = {385} \\quad SS_{C} = {554.83}$ <br>\n$T_{D} = {263} \\quad SS_{D} = {2976.83}$ <br>\n$T_{E} = {320} \\quad SS_{E} = {1097.33}$ <br>\n<br> State the Hypotheses <br> $H_0: \\mu_A = \\mu_B = \\mu_C = \\mu_D = \\mu_E$ <br> $H_1:$ At least one mean is different <br>\n<br> The decision criteria: <br><br>\n$F_{crit} = {4.43}, \\alpha = {0.01}$ <br><br>\n\nStage 1 Calculations: <br><br>\nCalculate the Degrees of Freedom <br>\n                    $$df_{total} = N - 1$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{total} = {30} - 1$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{total} = {29}$$ <br><br>\n                    $$df_{between} = k - 1$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{between} = {5} - 1$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{between} = {4}$$ <br><br>\n                    $$df_{within} = N - K$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{within} = {30} - {5}$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{within} = {25}$$ <br><br>\n                \nCalculate the Sum of Squares <br>\n                    $$SS_{total} = \\Sigma X^2 - \\frac{G^2}{N}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{total} = {113648} - \\frac{1774^2}{30}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{total} = {113648} - \\frac{3147076}{30}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{total} = {113648} - {104902.53}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{total} = {8745.47}$$ <br><br>\n                    $$SS_{within} = \\Sigma SS_{inside\\_each\\_condition}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{within} = {614.0 + 793.33 + 554.83 + 2976.83 + 1097.33}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{within} = {6036.32}$$ <br><br>\n                    $$SS_{between} = SS_{total} - SS_{within}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{between} = {8745.47} - {6036.32}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{between} = {2709.15}$$ <br><br>\n                    note: the other way to calculate $SS_{betwen}$ is: <br>\n                    $$SS_{between} = \\Sigma{\\frac{T^2}{n}} - \\frac{G^2}{N}$$ <br><br>\n                \nStage 2 Calculations: <br><br>\n                    Partition the Degrees of Freedom <br>\n                    $$df_{subjects} = n - 1$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{subjects} = {6} - 1$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{subjects} = {5}$$ <br><br>\n                    $$df_{error} = df_{within} - df_{subjects}$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{error} = {25} - {5}$$ <br>\n                    $$df_{error} = {20}$$ <br><br>\n                \nCalculate person sums and add a new column (*P*)\n```{=html}\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_3d0c2\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_3d0c2_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >ID</th>\n      <th id=\"T_3d0c2_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >A</th>\n      <th id=\"T_3d0c2_level0_col2\" class=\"col_heading level0 col2\" >B</th>\n      <th id=\"T_3d0c2_level0_col3\" class=\"col_heading level0 col3\" >C</th>\n      <th id=\"T_3d0c2_level0_col4\" class=\"col_heading level0 col4\" >D</th>\n      <th id=\"T_3d0c2_level0_col5\" class=\"col_heading level0 col5\" >E</th>\n      <th id=\"T_3d0c2_level0_col6\" class=\"col_heading level0 col6\" >P</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >1</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" >79</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row0_col2\" class=\"data row0 col2\" >53</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row0_col3\" class=\"data row0 col3\" >49</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row0_col4\" class=\"data row0 col4\" >49</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row0_col5\" class=\"data row0 col5\" >61</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row0_col6\" class=\"data row0 col6\" >291</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >2</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" >71</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row1_col2\" class=\"data row1 col2\" >69</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row1_col3\" class=\"data row1 col3\" >64</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row1_col4\" class=\"data row1 col4\" >54</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row1_col5\" class=\"data row1 col5\" >56</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row1_col6\" class=\"data row1 col6\" >314</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row2_col1\" class=\"data row2 col1\" >56</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row2_col2\" class=\"data row2 col2\" >58</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row2_col3\" class=\"data row2 col3\" >68</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row2_col4\" class=\"data row2 col4\" >77</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row2_col5\" class=\"data row2 col5\" >59</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row2_col6\" class=\"data row2 col6\" >318</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row3_col0\" class=\"data row3 col0\" >4</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row3_col1\" class=\"data row3 col1\" >59</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row3_col2\" class=\"data row3 col2\" >79</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row3_col3\" class=\"data row3 col3\" >79</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row3_col4\" class=\"data row3 col4\" >45</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row3_col5\" class=\"data row3 col5\" >31</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row3_col6\" class=\"data row3 col6\" >293</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row4_col0\" class=\"data row4 col0\" >5</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row4_col1\" class=\"data row4 col1\" >81</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row4_col2\" class=\"data row4 col2\" >47</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row4_col3\" class=\"data row4 col3\" >56</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row4_col4\" class=\"data row4 col4\" >35</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row4_col5\" class=\"data row4 col5\" >41</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row4_col6\" class=\"data row4 col6\" >260</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row5_col0\" class=\"data row5 col0\" >6</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row5_col1\" class=\"data row5 col1\" >80</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row5_col2\" class=\"data row5 col2\" >74</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row5_col3\" class=\"data row5 col3\" >69</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row5_col4\" class=\"data row5 col4\" >3</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row5_col5\" class=\"data row5 col5\" >72</td>\n      <td id=\"T_3d0c2_row5_col6\" class=\"data row5 col6\" >298</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n```\n\n$$SS_{subjects} = \\Sigma{\\frac{P^2}{k}} - \\frac{G^2}{N}$$ <br>\n$$SS_{subjects} = {\\frac{291^2}{5} + \\frac{314^2}{5} + \\frac{318^2}{5} + \\frac{293^2}{5} + \\frac{260^2}{5} + \\frac{298^2}{5}} - \\frac{1774^2}{30}$$ <br>\n$$SS_{subjects} = {\\frac{84681}{5} + \\frac{98596}{5} + \\frac{101124}{5} + \\frac{85849}{5} + \\frac{67600}{5} + \\frac{88804}{5}} - \\frac{3147076}{30}$$ <br>\n$$SS_{subjects} = {{16936.2} + {19719.2} + {20224.8} + {17169.8} + {13520.0} + {17760.8}} - {104902.53}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{subjects} = {105330.8} - {104902.53}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{subjects} = {428.27}$$ <br><br>\n                    $$SS_{error} = SS_{within} - SS_{subjects}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{error} = {6036.32} - {428.27}$$ <br>\n                    $$SS_{error} = {5608.05}$$ <br><br>\n                \nCalculate the Mean Squares <br>\n                $$MS_{between} = \\frac{SS_{between}}{df_{between}}$$ <br>\n                $$MS_{between} = \\frac{2709.15}{4}$$ <br>\n                $$MS_{between} = {677.29}$$ <br><br>\n            \n$$MS_{error} = \\frac{SS_{error}}{df_{error}}$$ <br>\n                    $$MS_{error} = \\frac{5608.05}{20}$$ <br> \n                    $$MS_{error} = {280.4}$$ <br><br>\n                \nCalculate the *F*-Ratio <br>\n                    $$F_{obt} = \\frac{MS_{between}}{MS_{error}}$$ <br>\n                    $$F_{obt} = \\frac{677.29}{280.4}$$ <br>\n                    $$F_{obt} = {2.42}$$ <br><br>\n                \nCalculate $\\eta^2$ <br>\n                    $$\\eta_p^2 = \\frac{SS{between}}{SS_{total} - SS_{subjects}}$$ <br>\n                    $$\\eta_p^2 = \\frac{2709.15}{{8745.47} - {428.27}}$$ <br>\n                    $$\\eta_p^2 = \\frac{2709.15}{8317.2}$$ <br> \n                    $$\\eta_p^2 = {0.33}$$ <br><br>\n                \nThe results: <br><br>\nfail to reject the null hypothesis, results not significant, <br><br> $F({4}, {20}) = {2.42}, p > {0.01}, \\eta_p^2 = {0.33}$\n\n\n\n",
